join  center
character: Hello! Welcome to the Nondescript Mountains, traveler. In this very short prototype, you must seek out what lies beyond the mountain range in front of you; it is where you can find more (extremely classified) dialogue from me. Find me before the world ends, traveler, we humbly depend on you. Best of luck!
character: Well, if it isn't the brave traveler that I encountered at the beginning of this prototype demo! I'm glad you were able to make it to the other side of the mountains in one piece; it is quite the journey from where you started. \
\
Now, for the super secret dialogue. The world is ending, as established by our previous conversation. The solution is actually quite simple\: the solution to the end of the world is you. Nothing more, nothing less. Persist, traveler, for a world without you in it is no world to be living in.